        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Tired of sales tools that feel like digital filing cabinets? I get it. I used to jump between my phone, email app, and a clunky CRM, losing precious time. Then I found Close, and it transformed my entire sales workflow into a single, powerful action hub. This isn't just another database—it's a command center designed to make you sell more, faster.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Close is a sales CRM built from the ground up for teams who live in the trenches of inside sales. It combines a visual pipeline, integrated calling, SMS, email, and smart automation into one seamless platform. And with its AI sales agent, Chloe, it doesn't just store data—it acts on it. I'm going to walk you through exactly how to harness it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
