              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " If you're a team, add members and assign roles. The permission settings are simple but powerful.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The goal here is to get all your sales activity flowing into one place. Within 15 minutes, you'll have a live workspace.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 2: Build Your Visual Sales Pipeline",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where Close's design genius shines. Your pipeline isn't a static list; it's a dynamic, drag-and-drop board that mirrors your real-world sales process.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Define Your Stages:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Go to Settings > Pipeline. Create stages like \"New Lead,\" \"Contacted,\" \"Qualified,\" \"Demo Scheduled,\" and \"Closed Won.\" Be specific to your business.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Customize Fields:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " For each stage, decide what information is critical. Need to track budget, decision timeline, or key pain points? Add those custom fields.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Visualize & Prioritize:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Now, drag leads between columns as they progress. The visual clarity is instant—you see bottlenecks and momentum in a glance. This pipeline is the heartbeat of your operation.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 3: Master the All-in-One Communication Hub",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is Close's killer feature. Stop switching tabs. Every call, email, SMS, and note lives inside the lead's profile.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Make & Log Calls Instantly",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Click the phone icon on any lead. Close has built-in calling with automatic recording and logging. After the call, it prompts you to log the outcome (e.g., \"Left Voicemail,\" \"Had Conversation\") and schedule a follow-up task. Everything is captured without extra work.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Send Emails & SMS with One Click",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Compose emails or text messages directly from the lead view. Templates let you fire off personalized messages in seconds. The SMS integration is particularly brilliant for quick check-ins or meeting reminders.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automate Your Outreach with Sequences",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Sequences are the engine of sales productivity. Here's how to build one:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. Go to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automation > Sequences",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
