        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes! Close has a built-in AI sales agent named Chloe. She's not an add-on but a core part of the platform. Chloe can automatically call and qualify new leads, book meetings, and update your CRM records, acting as a true extension of your sales team.",
